## ORF detection

Searches all 6 reading frames (3 forward, 3 reverse complement).
Reports: strand, frame, start position, end position, length (bp).
Results sorted by ORF length descending.

Default minimum ORF length: **100 bp** (adjustable with `--orf-min`).

---

## Complexity score

Linguistic complexity measures sequence diversity using k-mer frequency:

- Score of **1.0** = maximally complex (all possible 2-mers present)
- Score near **0** = low complexity / repetitive (e.g. AAAAAAA)

Useful for flagging low-complexity or repetitive regions.

